attributes.title: Jobs
attributes.visState:
{"title":"Jobs","type":"timelion","params":{"expression":"
.es(index=jobs, timefield='created_at',     metric='sum:duration')
.divide(60)
.divide(60)
.label('this week (hr)')
.color(lightgreen)
.lines(fill=1,width=1),


.es(offset=-1w, index=jobs, timefield='created_at',     metric='sum:duration')
.divide(60)
.divide(60)
.label('previous week (hr)')
.multiply(-1)
.color(green)
.lines(fill=1,width=1)

.title('Jobs duration over time')
.legend(columns=2, position=nw) ","interval":"auto"},"aggs":[]}
